Description: =========================
        Notebook-like Executables
        =========================
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nbex.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nbex
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/hoelzl/nbex.svg
